<!-- FAQ -->
<section class="section faq-section" id="faq">
    <div style="max-width:760px;margin:0 auto">
        <div class="center">
            <div class="section-tag">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="13" height="13" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="vertical-align:middle;margin-right:4px"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M9.09 9a3 3 0 0 1 5.83 1c0 2-3 3-3 3"/><path d="M12 17h.01"/></svg>
                FAQ
            </div>
            <h2 class="section-title">Frequently asked questions</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-list">
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
                    Who can join UniConnect?
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-caret-down faq-icon"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-a">UniConnect is exclusively for enrolled students at Philadelphia University. You register with your official university email, which is verified against the university registry. No one outside the university can create an account.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
                    How do I earn points?
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-caret-down faq-icon"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-a">You earn points by helping classmates — posting answers (+5), getting upvotes (+10 each), having your answer marked as Best Answer (+15), accepting tutor sessions (+20), getting 5-star ratings (+15), and daily logins (+2). You spend points posting questions (−10) or requesting tutoring sessions (−5).</div>
            </div>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <button class="faq-q" aria-expanded="false">
                    How do campus reward redemptions work?
                    <i class="ph-bold ph-caret-down faq-icon"></i>
                </button>
                <div class="faq-a">When you redeem points for a campus venue discount, a unique QR code is generated and sent to your university email. Take that QR code to the venue, show it at the counter, and the discount is applied instantly. Each code is single-use.</div>
